Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Lub-Lub in the Municipality of Dumangas, Province of Iloilo, to Barangay Monfort Norte
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 689
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Lub-Lub in the Municipality of Dumangas, Province of Iloilo, to Barangay Monfort Norte
Section 1. The name of Barangay Lub-lub in the Municipality of Dumangas, Province of Iloilo, is changed to Barangay Monfort Norte.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
